 <span data-ttu-id="aae72-103">使用时<xref:System.Data.Common.DbDataAdapter.Update%2A>，有两个事件发生的更新每个数据行。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="aae72-103">When using <xref:System.Data.Common.DbDataAdapter.Update%2A>, there are two events that occur for each data row updated.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="aae72-104">执行顺序如下所示：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="aae72-104">The order of execution is as follows:</span></span>  
  
